h1. s2-create-persistent-token

h2. Purpose

Creates a persistent token domain class for storing remember-me cookie information in the database. The general format is:

bc.
   grails s2-create-persistent-token <classname>

h2. Example

bc.
grails s2-create-persistent-token com.yourapp.PersistentLogin

h2. Description

This creates the domain class in the specified package, and also registers the name in @grails-app/conf/Config.groovy@, along with enabling persistent remember-me.
